        "TileImage": "$($repository 50356ca8-7372-4783-b143-31f2a2cd7c3d).Image",
        "Description": "Our client is the event organizer at today&apos;s party and wants everything planned to perfection. They have been in conflict with our target, a staff worker, whom they believe is incompetent and wastes a lot of time by taking frequent smoking breaks. This party is being attended by some of the most powerful and dangerous people in the world, so our client is willing to take no risks.\r\rThey want us to take out the target, but make it look like an accident. Absolutely no one else should be hurt.",
